{"id": 2704, "genre": 1000, "title": "你身上都有哪些介于积极和冷感之间的「被动热情」特质？", "description": "「被动热情」，一种「谈不上有多热衷，但是如果需要的话也能玩得转」的随遇而安型人格，非常适宜在当代生存。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Roi and Roi）", "record_count": 28453, "comment_count": 28, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201901021746464ZapRcUEz5xQqdMX.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-03T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5164, "title": "你身上都有哪些介于积极和冷感之间的「被动热情」特质？", "content": "你身上都有哪些「被动热情」特质？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 320344, "content": "不怎么主动跟人聊天，但别人找自己唠嗑也不会冷场", "image": "img/option/option/20190102222633ZyWbzxMQn03FGve4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320349, "content": "不跟风使用流行词汇，但看到就会搜一下是啥意思", "image": "img/option/option/20190102222946VTBOA4Sq20sdgDMj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320351, "content": "平时不看八卦新闻，但刷到了也会顺便吃吃瓜", "image": "img/option/option/20190102222925ghZfq1QNiL25WYyM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320357, "content": "不怎么热爱工作，然而一开始工作又能很快进入状态", "image": "img/option/option/20190102222913i41y7NqlWDFudJbO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320358, "content": "虽然知道某篇文章是广告，依然会捧个场点开看看", "image": "img/option/option/20190102222809pMRlrtO7PWZCE2gL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320359, "content": "不常刷社交媒体，但还是会给别人点赞", "image": "img/option/option/2019010222331045iKxnSINURFZ97B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320360, "content": "不常去朋友饭局，但是去了也能跟大家玩成一片", "image": "img/option/option/20190102222624ojJG7cufT94Lp8DB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320367, "content": "很少参加集体活动，但如果参加就会积极配合照顾大家", "image": "img/option/option/20190102222441RydNoXrhJwvEMxaH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}